## Probleme B5 — Avertissement "Host key has changed" apres reflash

**Statut :** Resolu
**Severite :** Faible

**Symptome :**
```
WARNING: REMOTE HOST IDENTIFICATION HAS CHANGED!
Host key verification failed.
```

**Cause :** Reflasher la micro SD genere une nouvelle cle SSH — l'ordi garde l'ancienne en memoire.

**Solution :**
```bash
ssh-keygen -R indigowing.local
ssh indigozafa@indigowing.local
```

**A faire a chaque fois qu'on reflashe la micro SD.**

